00:03:14,629 --> 00:03:16,310
They can become prosumers.

43
00:03:16,510 --> 00:03:17,637
They can interact.

44
00:03:17,837 --> 00:03:22,475
They can even, themselves,
organize the services:

45
00:03:22,675 --> 00:03:25,482
bike sharing services,
sharing economy.

46
00:03:25,682 --> 00:03:26,830
Things like that.

47
00:03:27,030 --> 00:03:33,476
From here follow the 3 main challenges
of services integration.

48
00:03:33,676 --> 00:03:37,636
The 1st challenge,
actually a traditional one,

49
00:03:37,836 --> 00:03:41,388
