84
00:06:19,795 --> 00:06:24,232
This is mainly geared at the weakest
customers,

85
00:06:24,432 --> 00:06:25,877
at the weakest citizens,

86
00:06:26,077 --> 00:06:28,016
who may not be able to afford

87
00:06:28,216 --> 00:06:31,151
or may not have access to these services.

88
00:06:31,351 --> 00:06:33,262
So there are 2 issues here.

