The 1st issue is the issue of accessibility.

90
00:06:37,123 --> 00:06:42,608
Think, for example, of information
about public transport.

91
00:06:42,808 --> 00:06:49,320
The new generation gets this information
all on their app on their smart phone,

92
00:06:49,520 --> 00:06:52,104
