these digital services.

102
00:07:36,503 --> 00:07:41,182
The 2nd issue is an issue
of affordability.

103
00:07:41,382 --> 00:07:44,556
This is a traditional issue.

104
00:07:44,756 --> 00:07:49,049
Some of the urban infrastructure services

105
00:07:49,249 --> 00:07:53,077
are essential, like water, like energy,

