00:08:51,555 --> 00:08:58,188
Also, in the digital era, this question
of affordability will continue to exist.

122
00:08:58,388 --> 00:09:04,128
The 3rd big challenge is the challenge
of quality of services.

123
00:09:04,328 --> 00:09:09,595
We have already said that
in the digital era,

124
00:09:09,795 --> 00:09:13,367
