125
00:09:13,567 --> 00:09:18,807
They may create, commence, communities,

126
00:09:19,007 --> 00:09:20,440
shared economy.

127
00:09:20,640 --> 00:09:22,400
They may offer services themselves.

128
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:26,615
They interact much more
with the services providers.

129
00:09:29,817 --> 00:09:31,996
The remains issues of competition.

130
00:09:32,196 --> 00:09:36,566
Remember when I talked about this tendency

131
